skills.name: KUNAI
desc: • Deals true damage to a single target.
• Remove Invincibility effects on the enemy.
• 75% Chance to Remove Damage Invulnerability effects on the enemy.
• Steal Fury and inflict Reduced Fury Generation of the target for 2 turns.

skills.name: RADIANT WIND
desc: • Deals true damage to all enemies.
• Reduce SPECIAL stat of all enemies to zero.
• 50% Chance to inflict Crave and Furious Burn on all enemies for 2 turns.
• Heal and grant an Extra Turn to self and a random ally.

skills.name: BOOK OF WIND
desc: Gains 100% Critical Strike Chance for the duration of battle. Grants Immunity to all allies for 2 turns at the start of battle.
